Welcome to 
        NCI Building Systems... 
At NCI Building Systems, Inc. (NYSE: NCS) we design, manufacture and market a comprehensive line of metal buildings and components for the nonresidential construction industry. Our products are used in new construction as well as retrofit work in virtually every sector – commercial, industrial, agricultural, institutional and governmental. We are also a leading metal coater and offer full-service coating capabilities for cleaning, treating, slitting and coating various flat-rolled metal coil substrates which are used for nonresidential construction applications by external customers and our own components and building groups, as well as for other industrial applications in the lighting, HVAC and appliance markets. Read more...

















